title: Discover the beauty Of Belgrade City through MSFS
description:
In this video we will look at the Belgrade City in Serbia which is now available in the MSFS marketplace. This package adds a lot of details as in multiple building types to the city which makes it really nice to fly over the city.

For a full overview of items added to the marketplace this week have a look at the video below:
